description:
Wednesday Addams (Christina Ricci) is the queen of darkness and the master of the death stare. From her deadpan one-liners to her perfectly timed acts of rebellion against all things cheerful, she embodies everything spooky and iconic. Alongside her equally macabre parents, Morticia (Anjelica Huston) and Gomez (Raul Julia), Wednesday’s darkly hilarious moments shine even brighter. 

Stream The Addams Family and Addams Family Values on Paramount+!
